Microservices:

Medical Dictionary
   Patients can use the in-app dictionary to look up the names of their prescription medicines and see which ailement they are for 
Prescription Management
   Patients can see all of their current prescriptions, dosages, and the days and times they need to take them. Patients can also see past presriptions.
Access Prescription
   Patients can check their current and past prescriptions
Request Prescription
   Patients can send a request to their primary physician to fill out a prescription for them
Request Prescription Refill
   Patient can request refills of current prescriptions 
Appointment Scheduler
   Patient can schedule online appointments with their primary physician
Secure Video Conferencing with WebEx
   The WebEx integration will allow patients to videocall their physician through the app
